                        <i class="bi bi-telephone-fill text-primary me-2 fs-5"></i>
                        <strong class="me-1">Phone:</strong>
                        +880 130 339 2175
                    </li>

                    <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="bi bi-linkedin text-primary me-2 fs-5"></i>
                        <strong class="me-1">LinkedIn:</strong>
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/imran-mahmud-ceo/" target="_blank"
